.section-grouping
  %h2 4. Importing an Image from a Provider  

  %p This task imports the image from a provider.

  %ol
    %li
    Click on the 
    %b Administer tab
    &rArr; <b>Environments:</b> this displays a list of your clouds.
    %li
    Click on name of cloud you wish to import your image into.
    %li
    Click the Import Image button.
    %li
    Choose a Provider Account from the drop-down selector.
    %li
    Enter the Image ID from your cloud resource provider.
    %li
    Enter a valid Image Name.
    %li
    Click Continue to import the component outline. 

  %p
    %center
      %a{ :href => "Images/Fedora 16 Images/import_image.png",
          :target => "_blank" }
        %img.thumbnail{ :src => "Images/Thumbnails/import_image_thumb.png",
